</p>
<p>This is probably the <em>weirdest</em> Twig template you'll ever see. It defines a bunch
of blocks that, together, contain <em>every</em> little bit or markup that's used for
<em>any</em> part of a form.</p>
<p>And here's how it works: when you render a piece of your form, Symfony opens this
template looks for a specific block, which varies depending on <em>what</em> you're rendering,
and then renders <em>just</em> that block to get that <em>one</em> little part of your form.</p>
<p>For example, when you render the <em>widget</em> for a <code>TextareaType</code> field, it looks for
a block called <code>textarea_widget</code> and executes <em>just</em> its code:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="cf4c54e75f">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
                        <span class="js-expand-all" data-range="1-372" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show All Lines" data-placement="top">
                <i class="fa fa-expand js-icon-load-more"></i>
                <i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin js-icon-loading"></i>
            </span>
            
            372 lines <span class="meta-divider"></span> <span title="vendor/symfony/symfony/src/Symfony/Bridge/Twig/Resources/views/Form/form_div_layout.html.twig">vendor/symfony/symfony/src/Symfony/Bridge/Twig/Resources/views/Form/form_div_layout.html.twig</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <table class="hljs code-block-table">
        <tbody class="js-tr-container">
                <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-expandable" data-range="1-32" data-last="0">
                <i class="fa fa-arrows-v js-icon-load-more" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show Lines" data-placement="left"></i>
                <i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin js-icon-loading"></i>
            </td>
            <td class="gap-line">
                                                    ... lines 1 - 32
                            </td>
            </tr>
    <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-displayed" data-line-number-displayed="33"></td>
            <td class="blob-code"></span><span class="hljs-template-tag">{%- <span class="hljs-name"><span class="hljs-keyword">block</span></span> textarea_widget -%}</span><span class="xml"></td>
            </tr>
    <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-displayed" data-line-number-displayed="34"></td>
            <td class="blob-code">    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">textarea</span> </span></span><span class="hljs-template-variable">{{ <span class="hljs-name">block</span><span class="hljs-params">('widget_attributes')</span> }}</span><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&gt;</span></span><span class="hljs-template-variable">{{ value }}</span><span class="xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">textarea</span>&gt;</span></td>
            </tr>
    <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-displayed" data-line-number-displayed="35"></td>
            <td class="blob-code"></span><span class="hljs-template-tag">{%- <span class="hljs-name"><span class="hljs-keyword">endblock</span></span> textarea_widget -%}</span><span class="xml"></td>
            </tr>
    <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-expandable" data-range="36-372" data-last="1">
                <i class="fa fa-arrows-v js-icon-load-more" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show Lines" data-placement="left"></i>
                <i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin js-icon-loading"></i>
            </td>
            <td class="gap-line">
